book:
Sphinx Client
Sphinx


 &reftitle.intro;


  This extension provides bindings for Sphinx search client library.
  Sphinx is a standalone search engine meant to provide fast,
  size-efficient and relevant fulltext search functions to other 
  applications. Sphinx was specially designed to integrate well with 
  SQL databases and scripting languages.
  Both Sphinx and its client library can be obtained from the
  official site



